 DRAMA

 September 12 at Academy of Fine Arts; 6.30 pm: Kalyani Natya Charcha Kendra presents Khwabnama. Direction: Kishore Sengupta. 

 September 14 at Academy of Fine Arts; 6.30 pm: Samakalin Shilpidal presents Chhayanat. Direction: Ambar Roy. 

