 FILM SHOW amp; DRAMA

 September 12 at Oxford Bookstore, 17 Park Street; 6.30 pm: Neo, in collaboration with Oxford Flash and Oxford Dialogue, presents the screening of The Hand of Fate (direction: Nirmalya Majumder) and the staging of Blues (direction: Amrita Panja); the screen and stage adaptations, respectively, of Katherine Mansfield?s The Fly. 

 EXHIBITION

 Till September 20 at 14/97 Golf Club Road; 12 noon - 8 pm: Sravasti offers Thakurbarir Poshak along with KeyaChaitali?s collection of katha, batik, dhakai, printed silk and cotton saris, kurtas, kutis, T-shirts, wrap-arounds and Saradins, with special emphasis on Podyo-Poshak based on Tagore?s poems. 

 Till September 18 at Toontooni, 10 Satyen Dutta Road: An exhibition of sarees and kurtas. 

